  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong> Vivid desktop widget </strong> </h2> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>This is a small box for mounting 3D models on the desktop, with four sides to display different models. It supports VMD format animations, let your model dance when dragged into the box<br></li><li></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Features </strong> </h2> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Directly load PMX and PMD format model files</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support VMD format animations[[/list]<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Provide two rendering styles: realistic and toon[[/list]<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Automatic addition of physics effects</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support for the Workshop</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Models can be popped out of the box for individual control</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong> Vivid desktop widget </strong> </h2> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>This is a small box for mounting 3D models on the desktop, with four sides to display different models. It supports VMD format animations, let your model dance when dragged into the box<br></li><li></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Features </strong> </h2> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Directly load PMX and PMD format model files</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support VMD format animations[[/list]<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Provide two rendering styles: realistic and toon[[/list]<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Automatic addition of physics effects</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support for the Workshop</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Models can be popped out of the box for individual control</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>",
